    dc:description "FIGURES 1-8. Tryphactothrips rutherfordi. (1) Female. (2) Male. (3) Head, male. (4) Pronotum, male. (5) Antennal segment II–IV, male. (6A) Antenna, female. (6B) Antenna, male. (7) Meso and metanota, male. (8) Abdominal tergites IV–V, male. (9) Abdominal sternites III–IV, male." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3626453/files/figure.png" ;
